1.2. Kim tra v x l d liu khuyt trong tp d liu:

Ta s thc hin thng k s lng v t l d liu khuyt cc bin, t x l la chn ra cc bin chnh phn tch. Tuy nhin, ta nhn thy rng cc gi tr khuyt khng cng loi. N c th l gi tr trng (hay rng) , gch ngang - ,.. gy kh khn cho vic thng k d liu khuyt . V th, thun tin ta chuyn i tt c chng thnh gi tr NA.
u tin, tm cc dng trng (hng c ton b cc gi tr l rng hoc ) trong d liu v chuyn chng thnh gi tr NA:

# Thay th tt c cc  trng trong d liu All_GPUs bng NA
All_GPUs[All_GPUs == ""] <- NA

Tip , tm cc gi tr trong dataframe c nh dng -(cc gi tr bt u bng k t xung dng theo sau l du - ) v chuyn chng thnh NA. Ta s dnglnh gsub() thay th - bng NA trong ton b dataframe.

# Thay th cc gi tr c nh dng "\n-" bng NA trong tt c cc ct ca All_GPUs 
All_GPUs[] <- lapply(All_GPUs, function(x) gsub("^\\n- $", NA, x))

Cui cng l thay th cc chui NA (N/A) thnh NA.

All_GPUs[All_GPUs == "NA"] <- NA

By gi cc d liu khuyt ng nht, ta tin hnh thng k s lng v t l d liu khuyt cc bin bng hm freq.na() trong th vin questionr.

# S dng hm freq.na()  tm tn sut NA trong d liu 
na_summary <- freq.na(All_GPUs) 
# Chuyn kt qu thnh mt data frame 
na_summary_df <- as.data.frame(na_summary) 
colnames(na_summary_df) <- c("NA_Count", "NA_Percentage")

1.3. La chn bin:
Sau khi loi b i cc bin c t l khuyt cao, ta s chn lc cc bin quan trng. Qua tm hiu, nhm nhn thy bin Memory_Speed l mt nhn t quan trng nh hng n hiu sut ca GPU. Tc xung nhp b nh l mt yu t thit yu trong hiu sut ca GPU, c bit i vi cc tc v yu cu GPU truy cp nhiu d liu. Tc xung nhp b nh cao hn c ngha l GPU c th truy cp b nh nhanh hn, dn n tng hiu sut.
Memory_Speed khng ch l v tc xung nhp, n c lin quan v chu nh hng trc tip bi Memory_Bandwidth.
V cc nhn t khc c nh hng vi mc khc nhau n Memory_Speed bao gm: Memory_Type,Memory_Bus,L2_Cache,Architecture,Process,Memory,Dedicated.
Ta c th ly thm bin Manufacturer so snh v nhn xt v Memory_Speed ca cc GPU cc nh sn xut khc nhau.

y l mt s ngun ti liu v c s ta c th tham kho tm hiu v cc bin c nh hng n Memory_Speed trong GPU.

Link: https://vibox.co.uk/blog/gpu-memory-clock-speed-vs-gpu-core-clock-speed
Link: https://www.hp.com/us-en/shop/tech-takes/does-ram-speed-matter

1.4. Lm sch d liu:
1.4.1 X l n v thun tin hn cho qu trnh phn tch, ta s b i n v ca cc bin nh L2_Cache, Memory,Memory_Bandwidth,Memory_Bus, Memory_speed, Process. Vic ny gip ng nht d liu, hp l ha phn tch v sau gip vic so snh v din gii d liu trn cc bin tr nn n gin hn.

# La chn cc bin cn xo n v
columns_to_clean <- c("L2_Cache","Memory","Memory_Bandwidth","Memory_Bus","Memory_Speed","Process")

#To hm thc hin xo n v  cc bin 
remove_units <- function(column) {
  # S dng gsub  xa tt c cc k t khng phi s (k c n v)
  cleaned_column <- gsub("[^0-9.]", "", column)
  # Chuyn i kt qu v kiu numeric
  cleaned_column <- as.numeric(cleaned_column)
  
  return(cleaned_column)
}

# p dng hm cho cc bin  chn
new_All_GPUs[columns_to_clean] <- lapply(new_All_GPUs[columns_to_clean], remove_units)

# Xc nh cc bin s v to mt khung d liu ch cha cc bin s
new_numeric_vars <- sapply(GPU_data, is.numeric)
numeric_data <- GPU_data[, new_numeric_vars]

# Tnh ton cc thng k m t cho cc bin s
summary_stats <- sapply(numeric_data, function(x) {
  c(
    Mean = mean(x),                   # Trung bnh
    SD = sd(x),                       #  lch chun
    Min = min(x),                     # Gi tr nh nht
    Q1 = quantile(x, 0.25),           # Phn v 25%
    Median = median(x),               # Trung v
    Q3 = quantile(x, 0.75),           # Phn v 75%
    Max = max(x)                      # Gi tr ln nht
  )
})

Nhm rt ra c mt s nhn xt v th histogram Phn Phi Memory Speed: th histogram th hin phn phi Memory Speed ca cc GPU trong tp d liu. Phn ln cc gi tr tp trung trong khong t 800 MHz n 1600 MHz, cho thy cc GPU ph bin thng hot ng trong phm vi tc ny. c bit, cc bins xung quanh 1500 MHz c tn sut xut hin cao nht, c th phn nh nhm sn phm ch lc hoc tiu chun ph bin trong ngnh sn xut GPU.

hai u ca phn phi, cc gi tr di 500 MHz v trn 2000 MHz xut hin rt t, biu th y l cc trng hp him. iu ny c th lin quan n cc GPU c c hiu nng thp hoc cc GPU cao cp dnh cho nhng ng dng c th.

Phn phi khng ng u ny cho thy s a dng v hiu nng ca cc GPU trong tp d liu. Tuy nhin, s tp trung mnh mt s khong gi tr gi rng mt vi dng sn phm chim u th ln trn th trng. hiu r hn v cc c im chi tit, vic iu chnh binwidth hoc phn tch cc thng s k thut tng ng c th hu ch. Ngoi ra, cn kim tra cc gi tr bt thng hai u phn phi loi b kh nng d liu li hoc ngoi l khng hp l.

ATI tp trung vo cc sn phm cao cp vi Memory Speed vt tri. Intel c phn khc r rng nhm hiu nng thp, ph hp vi GPU tch hp.

Nhm rt ra mt s nhn xt v th boxplot Memory Speed theo Dedicated GPU:

Non-Dedicated GPU (No): Phn b Memory Speed ca nhm ny rt hp, vi gi tr ch yu nm trong khong 1000 MHz. iu ny cho thy GPU tch hp c tc b nh thp v ng nht hn, ph hp vi vai tr h tr c bn thay v x l ha chuyn su.

Dedicated GPU (Yes): Phn b Memory Speed rng hn ng k, t khong 500 MHz n hn 2000 MHz. Trung v nm mc 1500 MHz, cao hn nhm Non-Dedicated GPU, cho thy GPU ri thng c hiu nng cao hn. Khong gi tr rng th hin s a dng trong phn khc sn phm, t cc GPU tm trung n cao cp.

GPU ri (Dedicated GPU) c tc b nh cao hn ng k so vi GPU tch hp, ph hp vi cc nhu cu x l ha phc tp v chuyn nghip. GPU tch hp (Non-Dedicated GPU) c hiu nng thp hn v t bin ng, ph hp vi cc ng dng c bn nh vn phng, xem phim, hoc chi game nh.

Da trn biu boxplot v Memory Speed (MHz) theo Memory Type, nhm rt ra cc nhn xt sau:

  1. Xu hng tng tc theo thi gian: Cc loi b nh i sau (GDDR5, GDDR5X, HBM-1, HBM-2) c tc cao hn ng k so vi cc loi i c (DDR, DDR2, DDR3). iu ny phn nh s tin b trong cng ngh b nh.

  2. Phn tn d liu: DDR, DDR2, DDR3: C tc thp, dao ng trong khong t 500 MHz n di 1000 MHz, vi mc phn tn tng i nh.GDDR4, GDDR5: C s phn tn ln hn, c bit GDDR5 vi tc tri di t khong 1000 MHz n hn 2000 MHz. GDDR5X: Tc tp trung hn mc cao, th hin hiu sut n nh.

  3. Ngoi l: Mt s im d liu ngoi hp (outliers) xut hin cc nhm DDR2, DDR3, GDDR5, c th i din cho cc sn phm ti u hoc khng tiu chun.

  4. B nh HBM (High Bandwidth Memory): HBM-1 v HBM-2 c tc thp hn nhiu so vi GDDR5X, nhng HBM thng c ti u cho bng thng thay v ch s MHz, v vy iu ny khng phn nh trc tip hiu nng.

Cng ngh b nh c s ci tin ng k theo thi gian, vi tc ngy cng cao cc th h mi. GDDR5 v GDDR5X hin ti c u th ln v hiu sut. Tuy nhin, c im ca tng loi b nh cn ph thuc vo mc tiu s dng (bng thng, hiu sut, hay tit kim nng lng).

Da trn kt qu t ma trn tng quan, ta c th a ra nhn xt v mi quan h gia Memory_Speed v cc bin khc:

Memory_Speed v Memory: C mi tng quan dng trung bnh vi tng quan = 0.49. iu ny cho thy rng tc b nh c s ph thuc ng k vo dung lng b nh. iu ny c ngha l khi dung lng b nh tng ln, tc b nh cng c th tng, v s thay i ny c th c phn nh trong cc m hnh hc my hoc phn tch d liu.

Memory_Speed v Memory_Bandwidth: Mi quan h gia bng thng b nh v tc b nh l rt quan trng, v tc b nh v bng thng c lin quan mt thit trong vic x l d liu. Memory_Bandwidth c th l yu t quan trng nh hng n Memory_Speed.

Memory_Speed v Memory_Bus: C mi tng quan rt yu vi tng quan = 0.02. iu ny cho thy rng rng bus b nh khng c nh hng ng k n tc b nh.

Memory_Speed v L2_Cache: L2_Cache c th nh hng n tc b nh, nhng mi quan h ny ph thuc vo nhiu yu t khc nh kin trc v quy trnh sn xut. Nu tng quan yu hoc khng r rng, c th ch ra rng b nh cache khng phi yu t quyt nh chnh.

Memory_Speed v Process:Mi quan h ny c th l nghch, c bit nu quy trnh sn xut (Process) c hn c th lm gim tc b nh.

Da trn biu phn tn ca bin Memory Speed theo cc bin Memory_Bandwidth, L2_Cache, Memory_Bus, Process, Memory, nhm rt ra mt s nhn xt:

C mt xu hng chung ch ra rng Memory Bandwidth cao hn c lin quan n Memory Speed cao hn. iu ny c ngha l khi bng thng b nh tng, tc b nh cng c xu hng tng.C th c mt s gi tr ngoi l trong d liu m mt s cu hnh b nh khng tun theo xu hng chung. Vic xc nh nhng gi tr ny c th cung cp thng tin chi tit v cc trng hp c th m hiu sut b nh lch khi chun mc.

C t im d liu hn cho kch thc b nh m L2 ln hn. Cc im ny phn tn nhiu hn v tc b nh, cho thy khi kch thc b nh m L2 tng ln, tc b nh thay i rng hn. Mc d biu cho thy s phn phi chung, nhng n khng ch ra mi tng quan r rng hoc mnh gia kch thc b nh m L2 v tc b nh. Tuy nhin, n cho thy tn ti nhiu cu hnh khc nhau vi kch thc b nh m v tc b nh khc nhau.

Mi quan h gia tc b nh v Bus b nh: C mt xu hng chung cho thy rng cc im d liu tp trung cc gi tr thp ca Memory Bus, tc l di 1000 Bits. iu ny cho thy cc h thng b nh c Bus b nh nh hn thng c s dng nhiu hn.

Mi quan h gia tc b nh v kch thc quy trnh: C mt xu hng chung cho thy rng khi kch thc quy trnh gim (tc l qu trnh sn xut cng tin tin), tc b nh c xu hng tng. iu ny cho thy cc cng ngh sn xut tin tin hn c th mang li hiu sut b nh cao hn. Phn b d liu: Cc im d liu phn b kh u trn th, cho thy s a dng trong kch thc quy trnh.

i vi phn ln d liu, Memory Speed (MHz) khng c xu hng tng r rt khi Memory (MB) tng. V vy tc b nh (Memory Speed) khng t l thun vi dung lng b nh (Memory). Mt s im c Memory ln vn duy tr Memory Speed tng i thp (di 1,000 MHz). Memory Speed phn tn mnh mc Memory nh (di 10,000 MB), trong khi mc Memory cao, s phn tn gim v t im d liu hn.

replace_na_with_group_mean <- function(data, group_col, target_col) {
  # Tnh ton gi tr trung bnh cho tng nhm trong ct Architecture
  group_means <- tapply(data[[target_col]], data[[group_col]], mean, na.rm = TRUE)
  
  # Thay th cc gi tr NA trong target_col vi gi tr trung bnh ca tng group
  data[[target_col]] <- mapply(function(x, group) {
    if (is.na(x)) {
      return(round(group_means[group], digits=0))
    } else {
      return(x)
    }
  }, data[[target_col]], data[[group_col]])
  
  return(data)
}

replace_na_with_mean_no_outliers <- function(data, group_col, target_col) {
  # Loi b gi tr ngoi lai bng cch s dng IQR
  remove_outliers <- function(x) {
    Q1 <- quantile(x, 0.25, na.rm = TRUE)
    Q3 <- quantile(x, 0.75, na.rm = TRUE)
    IQR_value <- Q3 - Q1
    lower_bound <- Q1 - 1.5 * IQR_value
    upper_bound <- Q3 + 1.5 * IQR_value
    x[x < lower_bound | x > upper_bound] <- NA
    return(x)
  }
  
  # p dng hm loi b ngoi lai theo tng nhm
  data[[target_col]] <- ave(data[[target_col]], data[[group_col]], FUN = function(x) remove_outliers(x))
  
  # Tnh ton gi tr trung bnh ca tng nhm sau khi loi b ngoi lai
  group_means <- tapply(data[[target_col]], data[[group_col]], mean, na.rm = TRUE)
  
  # Thay th cc gi tr NA trong target_col vi gi tr trung bnh ca tng group
  data[[target_col]] <- mapply(function(x, group) {
    if (is.na(x)) {
      return(round(group_means[group], digits = 0))
    } else {
      return(x)
    }
  }, data[[target_col]], data[[group_col]])
  
  return(data)
}

# p dng hm  thay th NA trong Memory_Bus v b qua ngoi lai
processed_data <- replace_na_with_mean_no_outliers(processed_data, "Memory_Type", "Memory_Bandwidth")

2.3.4. X l bin Memory

Thay v x l trn cc bin khc thay th bng gi tr trung bnh, bin Memory ta nhn thy cc gi tr memory tun theo mt s con s nht nh 128, 256, 512, V th bin Memory ta s thay th bng gi tr xut hin nhiu nht Memory_Type tng ng. Tuy nhin ta nhn thy ton b nhm ny u c Memory_Bandwidth l 34.1 v th ta s s dng gi tr mode ca Memory_Bandwidth = 34.1 ng vi ct Memory thay th.

  calculate_mode <- function(x) {
    x <- na.omit(x)  # B qua NA
    if (length(x) == 0) return(NA)
    unique_x <- unique(x)
    freq <- table(x)
    mode_value <- unique_x[which.max(freq)]
    return(mode_value)
  }

replace_na_with_mode_by_group <- function(data, target_col, group_col) {

  
  group_modes <- tapply(data[[target_col]], data[[group_col]], calculate_mode)
  
  data[[target_col]] <- mapply(function(memory, type) {
    if (is.na(memory)) {
      return(group_modes[[type]]) 
    } else {
      return(memory) 
    }
  }, data[[target_col]], data[[group_col]])
  
  return(data)
}

processed_data <- replace_na_with_mode_by_group(processed_data, "Memory", "Memory_Type")


replace_na_with_mode_for_specific_type <- function(data, target_col, group_col, group_value) {
  subset_data <- data[data[[group_col]] == group_value, target_col]
  
  mode_value <- calculate_mode(subset_data)
  
  data[[target_col]] <- ifelse(
    is.na(data[[target_col]]) & data[[group_col]] == group_value,
    mode_value,
    data[[target_col]]
  )
  
  return(data)
}

processed_data <- replace_na_with_mode_for_specific_type(processed_data, "Memory", "Memory_Bandwidth", 34.1)
